[admin] Hi friends, we are gathered here today to learn about Being Excellent.

Being Excellent to other spotters is pretty easy! In order to Be Excellent to Each Other, you just have to do the following:

1. If someone breaks the rules, report to admin before taking any action.
2. If someone has asked for context on a domestic post already, there's no need to ask again. 
3. If no one has asked for context on a spot, and it's a few hours old (over 5), report to admin. OP probably won't still be around.
4. If someone has broken the rules, report to admin. It's what we're here for.
5. If someone is being decidedly Not Excellent in the comments, report to admin.

Failure to Be Excellent will have most unTriumphant consequences. It's one of our top rules for a reason, friends!

Eventually the puppy ran after him but then I creeped over and was like, 'CAN I SAY HI TO YOUR PUPPY,' and the kid was like, 'Yeah of course!' and immediately the puppy, named Cooper, trotted over like this was par for the course during his day, then flopped over onto his back and let me rub his freckled pink puppy tum while his tongue fell a little bit out of his mouth and onto the grass.
